This is an implementation of a game called an m,n,k game. It's like an extended version of naughts and crosses. 


Required libraries and programs:
cmake
libSFML

run build.py

execution:
./main (board size nxn) (length of line to win) (difficulty -- corresponds to how deep the tree is searched)

e.g. ./main 3 3 x
is naughts and crosses
